      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Overall I find the portal useful for checking lab results, but the appointment scheduling workflow is confusing. I had to call the office twice because I wasn't sure my appointment was actually booked. The confirmation screen disappears too quickly and there is no email confirmation. Also, the mobile layout breaks on my Samsung Galaxy — buttons overlap and some text gets cut off. Would really appreciate a proper mobile-responsive design. On the positive side, the secure messaging feature works well and my doctor responds within 24 hours.",
